Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:37.40,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,At the fall cultural festival,\N I asked Koga to the folk dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:43.40,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,But Hideo's childhood friend, Sagawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:46.44,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,...challenged me, saying\N he wanted to hit my pitches.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:53.06,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,I got so engrossed in the duel that I\Ntotally forgot about my promise with Koga.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.49,0:01:56.58,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Koga, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.80,0:02:09.80,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HDEDEE5&\a5\fscx78\fscy82\move(360,170,360,170,35,-7)}Give It Your Best,\NKunimi Hiro !
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.43,0:02:25.60,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,I'm going to go, Third.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:11.93,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Would you like some ice cream ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:15.02,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:16.80,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:19.05,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,I don't need to \Nthank you today, do I ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:24.70,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Certainly, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:31.08,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,I'm glad that you\N actually came today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:32.93,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,As I said, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.93,0:03:34.69,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,I just got so engrossed in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:36.20,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,I'm not mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:38.50,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,I did want to do the folk dance with you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:44.88,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Besides, you're going to \Nspend the entire day with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:51.10,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,You're going to pay for everything, \Nand you'll do anything I ask, right ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:56.83,def2,..KINE:..,0,0,0,,Don't ask for too much.\N I have to pay for all this ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.83,0:04:00.13,def2,..GIRL:..,0,0,0,,If a cute girl is asking,\N you should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:02.68,def2,..KINE:..,0,0,0,,Even if you were cute, \Nyou're just my kiddy cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:05.90,def2,.GIRLA:..,0,0,0,,Hey, that looks so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:06.34,def2,..BOYA:..,0,0,0,,Huh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:07.65,def2,.GIRLA:..,0,0,0,,Can you buy that for me ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:09.21,def2,..BOYA:..,0,0,0,,I just bought you\N a similar one recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:12.00,def2,..GIRL:..,0,0,0,,Why are you looking\N envious, Ryutarou ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:14.53,def2,..KINE:..,0,0,0,,That's silly. \NWhy should I be envious ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:16.90,def2,..GIRL:..,0,0,0,,You're right.\N You're with me, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:19.00,def2,..GIRL...,0,0,0,,There's no way you'd\N be envious of anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:22.58,def2,..KINE:..,0,0,0,,What ? Why{would I not be envious if I'm} with you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:24.00,def2,..GIRL:..,0,0,0,,You're happy, aren't you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:35.30,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Now, Miss. You can tell me \Nany of your whimsical wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:38.45,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,My whimsical wish #1.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:43.50,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,You really want to ride this ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:44.76,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,My whimsical wish #2.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:48.64,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Let's not ride in the first row.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:49.51,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,#3.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:53.36,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,What ? It's a standing ride ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:54.50,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,#4.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:06.47,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,What was that ?\N It was scarier than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:09.17,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,I didn't know that you'd\N get scared so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:12.09,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,You don't act that way, \Nso I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:17.00,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Well, you're considered great if you can read a pitcher's mind just by looking at his face.{ial expressions.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:24.50,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing there ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.20,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Hey, popcorn.\NDo you want some ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:29.51,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,You're going to buy me some ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:30.25,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:31.30,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:32.00,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:56.29,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Kunimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:00.76,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,You didn't force yourself to come with me, right ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:05.40,def2,..KINE:..,0,0,0,,It was an obligation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:07.46,def2,..KINE:..,0,0,0,,Obligation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:11.33,def2,..GIRL:..,0,0,0,,Don't put on an act. \NI know you're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:14.40,def2,..KINE:..,0,0,0,,Hey, how old are you ? How old ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:18.20,def2,..KINE:..,0,0,0,,There's no way I could enjoy\N being with a cheeky kid like you !
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:19.40,def2,..KINE:..,0,0,0,,Shut up and eat !
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.12,0:06:23.93,def2,..KINE:..,0,0,0,,Huh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:28.50,def2,..GIRL:..,0,0,0,,That show of anger is really an expression of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:35.25,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,I'm happy that it's\N an amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:36.05,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,What ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.05,0:06:38.00,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Instead of the folk dance, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:42.60,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Weekdays are great.\N It's not crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:44.30,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:09.51,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Koga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.51,0:07:10.00,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Yes ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:14.87,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,The carp here are so gluttonous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:18.93,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:24.43,def2,.POLICE:.,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:32.12,def2,.POLICE:.,0,0,0,,You're high school \Nstudents, aren't you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,0:07:33.40,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:35.82,def2,.POLICE:.,0,0,0,,What about school ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:38.70,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,We had a cultural festival on Sunday, so we have an off day today instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:41.13,def2,.POLICE:.,0,0,0,,You're off today ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.13,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:43.05,def2,.POLICE:.,0,0,0,,Fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:44.54,def2,.GIRLA:..,0,0,0,,Let's go there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:46.70,def2,..BOYA:..,0,0,0,,The surprise house ? Don't be\N surprised by your own face, okay ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:48.30,def2,.GIRLA:..,0,0,0,,That's mean. \NThat goes for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:50.03,def2,..BOYA:..,0,0,0,,But really, some of those\N make you look scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:54.00,def2,.POLICE:.,0,0,0,,Nowadays, high school kids should hold hands. You two should, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.00,def2,.POLICE:.,0,0,0,,Right ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:02.58,def2,.POLICE:.,0,0,0,,Amusement park. It's so joyful.\N Amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:04.93,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,What was that about ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:06.64,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,You know ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:07.30,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:11.99,def2,..KINE:..,0,0,0,,Let go of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:15.30,def2,..GIRL:..,0,0,0,,Don't be bashful. \NWe're just holding hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:16.65,def2,..KINE:..,0,0,0,,I'm not being bashful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:22.58,def2,..GIRL:..,0,0,0,,Ryutarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:24.30,def2,..GIRL:..,0,0,0,,You want one ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:28.88,def2,..KINE:..,0,0,0,,I don't want one. \NJust finish it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:31.99,def2,..KINE:..,0,0,0,,Oh, man.\N My clothes got sticky, too !
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:34.22,def2,.POLICE:.,0,0,0,,You two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:35.69,def2,.POLICE:.,0,0,0,,What happened to school ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:36.50,def2,..KINE:..,0,0,0,,What ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:43.24,def2,..KINE:..,0,0,0,,Well, we have a day off  \Nbecause of the cultural festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:44.27,def2,..KINE:..,0,0,0,,Right ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:49.30,def2,..KINE:..,0,0,0,,One boy ticket and \None girl ticket, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:51.17,def2,..GIRL:..,0,0,0,,You mean one adult\N and one child, right ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:53.42,def2,..GIRL:..,0,0,0,,Why are you so flustered ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:54.59,def2,..KINE:..,0,0,0,,Shut up !
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:09:01.60,def2,.POLICE:.,0,0,0,,Leaves turning red. Walking while holding hands. The autumn sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:03.00,def2,.POLICE:.,0,0,0,,That's a great haiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:05.83,def2,..KINE:..,0,0,0,,What is that about ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:33.80,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,{\pos(327,437)}Hey, what's your next whim ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:39.68,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG:..,0,0,0,,Jumping over the puddles one by one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:39.90,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,{\pos(317,434)}I was just trying to think \Nof one. My next whim is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:46.65,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG:..,0,0,0,,...I want to get past a hardship like that.{How I wish I could leave sorrow things behind in the same way}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:41.76,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,{\pos(325,436)}Umm, what's the next one ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:42.58,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,436)}It's #23.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:44.16,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,{\pos(326,437)}You've been counting, Kunimi ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:44.90,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,{\pos(318,436)}I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:55.20,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG:..,0,0,0,,Like you, I run up the pedestrian bridge...{I climb up a pedestrian bridge, mimicking you}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.66,0:09:50.84,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,436)}Is that it ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:53.15,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,{\pos(323,437)}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:56.12,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,{\pos(328,436)}I'm saving that one for last.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:57.99,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,{\pos(326,438)}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:10:03.15,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG:..,0,0,0,,...keeping up with the sunny sky, I want to feel courageous.{I'd like to feel that I'm equal with a clear sky}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:05.70,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,{\pos(334,436)}I guess we're riding that one, too ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.15,0:10:09.65,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG:..,0,0,0,,"How does he keep such a nice facial expression ?"{"How good he looks,"}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:18.30,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,I thought with frustration, when I met you.{When we met, I felt so strongly that it was almost frustrating}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:15.19,def2,..BOYA:..,0,0,0,,{\pos(322,435)}It was a mirror, but you\N were acting like it was real.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.40,0:10:18.40,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,{\pos(318,436)}Kunimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:19.11,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,436)}Yeah ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:21.90,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG:..,0,0,0,,"I'm definitely glad we met."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:26.00,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG:..,0,0,0,,Let's stay strong and move forward.{I'm definitely glad we've metlet's go with such conviction}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:25.66,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,{\pos(316,437)}Hmm. {sticks out his tongue}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:29.41,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,434)}Hey, it's well-made.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:33.70,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG:..,0,0,0,,When I'm by myself I notice, that, beyond this dazzling feeling...{When I notice I am alone, at the end of bright memories}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:41.50,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,...yesterday, today, and tomorrow, there are more and more smiles.{Yesterday, today and tomorrow, my smiles multiply}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:48.50,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,Just by looking at you, see ? My eyes will look kinder.{Just by looking at you, you see, my gaze becomes kinder.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.46,0:10:44.80,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,434)}Hey, Koga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:47.94,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,{\pos(318,437)}This one looks interesting, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:49.44,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:52.00,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:00.99,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Wait up, Kunimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:27.12,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Where are you, Kunimi ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:39.90,yamato,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H313275&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(293,151)}Aim for the Koushien
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:47.85,yamato,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H313275&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(309.333,157.333)}Aim for the Koushien
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:26.90,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\a5\fscx67\fscy58\pos(564,323)}No Reentry\NAllowed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:08.23,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,I can't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:13.20,def2,SECURITY:,0,0,0,,What happened to your boyfriend ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:15.27,def2,SECURITY:,0,0,0,,You two lost each other ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:16.60,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:19.80,def2,SECURITY:,0,0,0,,That's why I told \Nyou to hold hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:26.22,def2,SECURITY:,0,0,0,,A minor cross-up\N leads to the end of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.84,0:13:30.80,def2,SECURITY:,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:38.30,def2,..GIRL:..,0,0,0,,I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:45.90,def2,..GIRL:..,0,0,0,,The lost child is a long-haired, lecherous-looking high school boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:48.12,def2,..GIRL:..,0,0,0,,He's totally useless without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:50.23,def2,..GIRL:..,0,0,0,,He's aimless and helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:52.44,def2,..GIRL:..,0,0,0,,Really, he's such a handful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:24.93,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Why are you making such a face ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:29.70,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,I was afraid that \Nyou'd left me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:32.75,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,That maybe I asked for too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:35.86,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,I promised to spend the day with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.86,0:14:37.11,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Honestly ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:40.23,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Honestly. You should have confidence in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:45.40,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H7AC5F1&\fscx192\fscy142\move(180,73,142,48,6,2884)}Ring Toss
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:45.40,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H7AC5F1&\move(163,187,145,180,6,2884)}Three rings per game, 200 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:45.40,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HCDCCBC&\move(466,427,469,449,6,2884)}The prize of the ring toss must\Nbe completely inside the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:47.99,def2,..MAN:...,0,0,0,,Here are the three rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:56.99,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,That one !
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:03.08,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:05.71,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,I wanted to come to\Nthe amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:09.36,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,At an amusement park, we can go back to feeling like children.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:13.35,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,I thought I'd be able\Nto see your everyday self.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:22.80,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Well, it's a date today.\NI guess I'm a little tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:24.30,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,A date ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:26.87,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Don't repeat what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.29,0:15:33.08,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,You're being bashful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:39.70,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H44449D&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fscx185\fscy123\pos(326,461)}Peerless
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:43.29,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,You can throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:45.65,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Why ? I wanted this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:46.97,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:48.06,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,I'm being honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:52.37,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Well, what's next ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:56.92,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Shall we go for the one we've saved ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:57.62,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:23.19,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Wow, it's a great view !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:27.51,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:34.49,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Look, Kunimi !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:36.66,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,I'll see it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.36,0:16:40.20,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Are you afraid of heights ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:42.48,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,A little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:51.75,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,But you said you\N wanted to ride this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:54.56,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,You looked like you wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.13,0:17:01.51,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Don't move ! \NIt's losing balance !
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:06.05,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,When I first met you, it was spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:10.00,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}Were you able to burn it ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.41,0:17:13.27,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}Kunimi Hiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:19.04,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}I'm Koga Haruka, the manager for the Senkawa High School Baseball Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:34.58,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,It's coming up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:35.34,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,What is ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:44.25,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Look, Kunimi !
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:17:55.55,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,To tell the truth, I wanted us to see this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.75,0:17:58.51,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,What is it ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:29.10,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,You wanted juice ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:31.30,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:57.96,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:02.94,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,It feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:17.08,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:28.89,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Since when ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:31.18,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,It's been like this since\N I woke up this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:35.01,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,That's stupid ! You should\N have called me and canceled !
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:37.20,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,No way ! \NIt would be such a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.20,0:19:39.44,def2,.HARUKA..,0,0,0,,You're paying for everything today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:40.95,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,You're the daughter\N of a company president.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:42.60,def2,.KUNIMI..,0,0,0,,There's no need to be stingy !
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:47.48,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,I've been looking forward to this, since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:53.78,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,We're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.68,0:19:56.55,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,You promised to \Nspend the day with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.66,0:20:02.40,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Today isn't the only off day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:05.15,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,If you don't mind splitting the tab, I'll go out with you anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:10.48,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Really ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:11.50,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.04,0:20:13.68,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Then we'll go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:30.67,def2,..KINE:..,0,0,0,,In five years, you'll be cuter, even if not as cute as Koga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.11,0:20:49.16,def2,..KINE:..,0,0,0,,It's hot !
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:54.20,def2,..KINE:..,0,0,0,,What did you do that for ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:56.70,def2,..KINE:..,0,0,0,,It made a mark on my cheek !
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.70,0:20:57.46,def2,..KINE:..,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:01.69,def2,..GIRL:..,0,0,0,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:10.13,def2,..KINE:..,0,0,0,,Koga ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:25.20,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Oh, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.96,0:21:28.58,def2,SECURITY:,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.55,0:21:34.38,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,Could you take a photo of us ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:42.30,def2,SECURITY:,0,0,0,,Today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:44.65,def2,..SONG...,0,0,0,,Romance begins at the amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:48.20,def2,..SONG...,0,0,0,,And I make happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:49.25,def2,SECURITY:,0,0,0,,Too many syllables.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:51.20,def2,SECURITY:,0,0,0,,Say cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.17,0:21:57.40,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,You shouldn't take\N a photo of us like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.40,0:21:59.99,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,It's to commemorate our first date.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.99,0:22:01.15,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:03.41,def2,.HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,I look forward to spending time with you.
