Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.82,0:23:00.13,Karaoke Translation op,..EDSONG:..,0,0,0,,{\pos(297.778,463.111)}I thought with frustration, when I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.30,0:23:03.43,Karaoke Translation op,..EDSONG:..,0,0,0,,{\pos(304,462.222)}"I'm definitely glad we met."
